Many large theaters, such as those on Broadway, also stopped all performances.
Some artists have sought ways to continue to create and share their work on the Internet as an alternative to traditional live performances, such as online and live concerts or online festivals created for artists to perform, broadcast and promote their works.
Online, many coronavirus-themed internet memes have spread as many favor humor and distraction in the face of uncertainty.
